    <title>vps+ss实现翻墙</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/02/11/chicken/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/02/11/chicken/</id>
    <published>2018-02-11T10:19:45.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-11T12:43:18.224Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="vps的简单搭建（2-5-monthly）"><a href="#vps的简单搭建（2-5-monthly）" class="headerlink" title="vps的简单搭建（2.5$monthly）"></a>vps的简单搭建（2.5$monthly）</h1><blockquote><p>自从建了博客以后就很久没有写了，😅。现在想写都快把语法给忘完了</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2018/02/11/chicken/chicken.jpg" alt="log"></p><p></p><p><br>　　一直想翻个墙，但是奈何找不到代理服务器，听说蓝灯很好用但是我下了也上不了网。还好姚大仙说买个vps自己搭个也很快，所以我也自己学着搭了个。<br><br>　　想想很麻烦，但是其实跟着教程走，一下子就搭好了，虽然有点不明所以。<br></p><br>————比较麻烦的是<p></p><ul><li>要找个详细的教程</li><li>配置多个用户的时候需要折腾下，这个纯属个人</li></ul><h3 id="下面就是教程的连接，找了好多，就这个最好。（如果有经验可跳过，我在后面提取了代码）"><a href="#下面就是教程的连接，找了好多，就这个最好。（如果有经验可跳过，我在后面提取了代码）" class="headerlink" title="下面就是教程的连接，找了好多，就这个最好。（如果有经验可跳过，我在后面提取了代码）"></a>下面就是教程的连接，找了好多，就这个最好。（如果有经验可跳过，我在后面提取了代码）</h3><ol><li><a href="http://blog.csdn.net/sonpking/article/details/78910720" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>超级连接，搭建教程</strong></a>-<code>里面已经说明的很全面了</code><br><br></li><li><a href="https://my.vultr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>点击vultr</strong></a>的注册，网上太多了，就不说明了，用支付宝付就行了(<code>选纽约的还有2.5$</code>)<br><br></li><li>远程连接<font style="color: red">putty.exe</font>  和 <font style="color: red">shadowsocks.exe</font>可以去网上下在，或者找我百度网盘传<br> </li></ol><h3 id="主要还是教程中可能遇到的问题点"><a href="#主要还是教程中可能遇到的问题点" class="headerlink" title="主要还是教程中可能遇到的问题点"></a>主要还是教程中可能遇到的问题点</h3><p></p><p></p><ul><li><p><font style="color: red">putty</font>就是等于一个远程连接服务端的工具，和桌面的远程连接一样的意思，只要先连上就能安装了</p></li><li><p><font style="color: red">shadowsocks</font> 就是安装在电脑上的客户端，<br>　　<font style="color: blue">（如果服务端配置好了）</font>只要输入用户密码就能实现翻墙了，很简单 </p></li><li><p>在配置多个用户的时候，会出现就原来的端口可行，第二第三都访问不了，那是因为没有关闭防火墙（例如12258端口）</p><ul><li>运行如下代码：<ul><li><font style="color: green">firewall-cmd –permanent –zone=public –add-port=12258/tcp</font></li><li><font style="color: green">firewall-cmd –permanent –zone=public –add-port=12258/udp</font></li><li><font style="color: green">firewall-cmd –reload</font></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>添加用户完以后是一定要重启ss的 </p><ul><li><font style="color: green">/etc/init.d/shadowsocks-python restart</font></li></ul></li><li><p>安装教程说的，用户限流：当超过流量的时候，会把帐号密码删除，所以帐号就无效了<br><br>当 <font style="color: green">bsp -r</font> 的时候,就会对限流账户初始化，并重新添加密码[又能正常使用了]<br></p><br><hr><br><hr><p></p><h2 id="对于已经装过的-就直接复制粘贴代码吧"><a href="#对于已经装过的-就直接复制粘贴代码吧" class="headerlink" title="对于已经装过的,就直接复制粘贴代码吧"></a>对于已经装过的,就直接复制粘贴代码吧</h2></li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 安装ss</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">1.</span> wget --no-check-certificate -O shadowsocks-all.sh https:<span class="comment">//raw.githubusercontent.com/teddysun/shadowsocks_install/master/shadowsocks-all.sh</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">2.</span> chmod +x shadowsocks-all.sh</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">3.</span> ./shadowsocks-all.sh <span class="number">2</span>&gt;&amp;<span class="number">1</span> | tee shadowsocks-all.log</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">4.</span> 配置多个用户端口</span><br><span class="line">  　- 在/etc/shadowsocks-python/config.json 把端口和密码删除，换上如下</span><br><span class="line">  　- vi config.json 修改</span><br><span class="line">  　- 按 i 进行编辑</span><br><span class="line">  　-<span class="string">"port_password"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      　<span class="string">"899565"</span>: <span class="string">"sd4asdwe"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      　<span class="string">"14415"</span>: <span class="string">"45dasd4"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      　<span class="string">"18745"</span>: <span class="string">"45dfgsd"</span></span><br><span class="line">  　　  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">- 完成后按 esc 退出编辑，然后输入 ：wq 保存的意思</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">6.</span> 需要/etc/init.d/shadowsocks-python restart 重启</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">7.</span> 开防火墙</span><br><span class="line">- bsp安装</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">1.</span> git clone https:<span class="comment">//github.com/edboffical/bsp.git</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">2.</span> cd bsp</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">3.</span> chmod <span class="number">775</span> install</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">4.</span> ./install</span><br><span class="line">--bsp操作</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">1.</span> 添加</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> bsp -p <span class="number">8989</span> -P <span class="number">123456</span> -s <span class="number">100</span> -a -A -j</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">2.</span> 删除</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> bsp -p <span class="number">8989</span> -d -D -R</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">3.</span> 启动 （一次就够了）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> bsp --start</span><br><span class="line">- 这是以后的操作</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">4.</span> 初始化</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> bsp -r</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="number">5.</span> 查看流量使用情况</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> bsp -p <span class="number">8989</span> -c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>还是嫌麻烦的有缘人，可以直接找我要一个用户😳</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
